Library dependencies
====================
Rpi-hw has no dependencies.


Building with CMake
===================
 $ cd <SOURCES>
 $ cmake ./ -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<PATH>
 $ make
 # make install


Linking with Rpi-hw
=======================
To link:

 $ g++ `pkg-config --libs --cflags rpi-hw` <SOURCE> -o <BIN>


 
